description:
Question management pages query 'prisma.organizationMember' but database schema only defines 'UserRole' model. This causes complete failure of question bank features.

**Impact:** P0 - CRITICAL - Question banks cannot be accessed
**Affected Files:**
- apps/staff/app/dashboard/questions/[id]/page.tsx (line 18-21)
- apps/staff/app/dashboard/questions/[id]/questions/new/page.tsx (line 23-26)
- apps/staff/app/dashboard/questions/[id]/questions/[qid]/page.tsx (line 23-26)

**Fix Required:**
Replace all organizationMember queries with userRole queries:

```typescript
// Current (BROKEN)
const membership = await prisma.organizationMember.findFirst({
  where: { userId: session.user.id },
  include: { organization: true }
});

// Should be
const userRole = await prisma.userRole.findFirst({
  where: { userId: session.user.id },
  include: { organization: true }
});
```

**Effort:** 1-2 hours (search and replace in 3 files)
**Blocks:** All question bank testing and functionality
